<section id="domain-about" class="sandbox-domain" data-domain="about" data-active="false">
  <span class="status-pill">Product context, credits, and identity.</span>
  <div class="sandbox-section-title">Product</div>
  <p>Thin runtime harness for one MagicMirror module.</p>
  <span class="status-pill">Supported surface is intentionally narrow but MagicMirror-faithful.</span>
